page.title: 02Katie Jenkins' Day
page.content: On a holiday day I wake up about nine o'clock. I read to about ten o'clock. Around that time my mum gets fed up with calling me. I get dressed and go downstairs for breakfast. By that time it is half past ten and the stereo is on full blast. I put a good record on like "Material Girl" or "kiss Me". I then have a shower. After that I take the dog for a walk across the fields. We come back and have dinner. When I have finished I go out to the garden. I play catch with the dog then I clean out the rabbit hutch. My rabbit is grey and white and really cuddly; That's why I call it Cuddles. My dog is called Tina for no reason; it just came to me when I was thinking what to call it. After I finish cleaning out the hutch I call for my best friend at home, Jo, and my other best friend at home, Wendy.
